To run the tests:

$ PYTHONPATH=tests/ DJANGO_SETTINGS_MODULE=talks.settings_test pybot -i todo tests/

This will run tests using firefox. You can use another browser passing BROWSER env variable. See Selenium docs for details.
Open report.html to see the results

Documentation:
https://code.google.com/p/selenium/
http://robotframework.org/robotframework/latest/RobotFrameworkUserGuide.html
http://rtomac.github.io/robotframework-selenium2library/doc/Selenium2Library.html

